The team will not work with teletext.
The remote will only control televisions.
The corporate color and design must be incorporated into the design of the remote.
The remote will have buttons for the following functions: on and off , channel up and down , volume up and down , and entering channel numbers.
The remote has to look good and be easy to use.
The target demographic is people aged fifteen to thirty five.
The remote will use an infra-red sensor.
The remote will use regular batteries.
